      <title>特鲁多的保守党对手承诺减缓加拿大人口增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trudeau-s-tory-rival-pledges-to-slow-canada-s-population-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[保守党领袖皮埃尔·波利耶夫 (Pierre Poilievre) 目前被认为是下届加拿大大选的获胜热门人选，他表示，加拿大需要减缓人口增长速度，以更好地适应住房、就业和医疗保健的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trudeau-s-tory-rival-pledges-to-slow-canada-s-population-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:46:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列紧张局势加剧，伊朗核储备增加</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/iran-s-nuclear-stockpile-grows-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合国监督机构称，伊朗核燃料水平在过去三个月内有所上升，有可能加剧紧张局势，并有可能引发地区战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/iran-s-nuclear-stockpile-grows-amid-simmering-israel-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:37:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥选举法院确认莫雷纳在国会的实力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mexico-s-electoral-court-confirms-morena-s-strength-in-congress</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥最高选举法院确认，执政党联盟将在众议院保持绝对多数，并且在六月大选后仅差几个席位就能在参议院取得同样的结果。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/mexico-s-electoral-court-confirms-morena-s-strength-in-congress</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:31:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>纽森将决定是否为加州无证移民提供住房贷款援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/california-s-home-loan-help-for-undocumented-immigrants-goes-to-newsom-s-desk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加州立法者已向州长加文·纽瑟姆提交了一份法案，该法案将扩大由州政府支持的首付援助计划，以惠及想要买房的无证移民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/california-s-home-loan-help-for-undocumented-immigrants-goes-to-newsom-s-desk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>致命袭击后德国加强武器和驱逐规定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/germany-tightens-weapons-deportation-rules-after-fatal-attack</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在上周发生致命的持刀袭击事件后，德国总理奥拉夫·朔尔茨领导的执政联盟同意了一项方案，旨在加强对刀具等武器的监管，并降低驱逐犯罪寻求庇护者的门槛。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/germany-tightens-weapons-deportation-rules-after-fatal-attack</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 15:19:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>赞比亚计划让国有企业拥有 30% 的关键矿产矿权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/zambia-plans-state-firm-to-own-30-of-critical-minerals-mines</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚计划成立一家投资公司，控制未来矿山至少 30% 的关键矿产产量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/zambia-plans-state-firm-to-own-30-of-critical-minerals-mines</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:53:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称将宣布一项计划，让美国成为“加密之都”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普似乎正在更深入地涉足数字资产世界，他表示将公布计划，确保美国成为“全球加密之都”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-says-he-ll-announce-a-plan-to-make-us-the-crypto-capital-of-the-planet</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:50:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国对每架未全面升级的 F-35 战机扣留 500 万美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国防部的 F-35 项目办公室和洛克希德马丁公司表示，对于每架尚未配备符合规格的先进硬件和软件的 F-35 飞机，五角大楼将向洛克希德马丁公司扣留 500 万美元。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/us-withholding-5-million-for-each-f-35-lacking-full-upgrade</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:40:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普称其修改后的起诉书违反了美国政策。以下是他错在哪里</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-s-claim-justice-department-violated-policy-with-indictment-is-debunked</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 正在利用其最新的妨碍选举起诉书重新引发对美国特别检察官的政治偏见投诉，理由是政府的政策是避免在选举前采取可能影响结果的行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-29/trump-s-claim-justice-department-violated-policy-with-indictment-is-debunked</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 29 Aug 2024 14:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国两党支持非洲关键矿产计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-sees-bipartisan-backing-for-africa-critical-minerals-projects</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务院一位高级官员向非洲各国政府保证，即使在政府更迭之后，通过发展非洲基础设施来帮助对抗中国影响力的举措仍将继续。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-28/us-sees-bipartisan-backing-for-africa-critical-minerals-projects</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 28 Aug 2024 15:54:53 GMT</pubDate>
